description.en:
"After establishing our coin, we have a few ideas which involve worthy causes.
One of which is a dire need in South Africa of baby drop boxes. (Might reach out to other countries that are in need too)
There are thousands of babies that are abandoned by their mothers right after birth, most of them end up in drain pipes or rubbish dumps, etc.
By helping to create/sponsor these baby drop boxes, we can save several babies from death."
